Subject: Remove message-id security leaks section of manual

The message-id generator has been changed to use a combination of time
and random components for the left side.

Upstream-commit: https://gitlab.com/muttmua/mutt/commit/ee2b9d1dd8963a7b5b469ddfd8609f9a40bd5157

Co-authored-by: Kevin McCarthy <kevin@8t8.us>
